  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist if you like it!</h1><p>Thanks for the support!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/81596161ec0fc4fce390df449dd9d392.poster.avif?t=1738838728\" width=360 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/81596161ec0fc4fce390df449dd9d392.webm?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/81596161ec0fc4fce390df449dd9d392.mp4?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crystal Eyes is an Indie <strong>pixelart adventure game with RPG touches.</strong> Inspired by the 90's graphic adventure games like Monkey Island and classic SNES rpgs like Secret of Mana. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/3ffdf39b9fbfcadded67e8bb11060e2a.poster.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/3ffdf39b9fbfcadded67e8bb11060e2a.webm?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>The game is <strong>narrative</strong> and <strong>exploration</strong> driven, but <strong>combats</strong> are dynamic and fun, involving the use of swords, magic and armors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/c1f7737763768d5098abe5eb9b6d81a8.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>The game includes in-game HELP POINTS for the chill players that just want to enjoy an interesting narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/b89c524b7c138d8fac20214f705ab758.poster.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/b89c524b7c138d8fac20214f705ab758.webm?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/b89c524b7c138d8fac20214f705ab758.mp4?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player will play as an adventurous kid that gets involved in a series of events that will affect the history of the world where he lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/7bac3ea8bf2bc73e13106dfb071a27c0.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crystal Eyes is an Indie <strong>pixelart adventure game with RPG touches.</strong> Inspired by the 90's graphic adventure games like Monkey Island and classic SNES rpgs like Secret of Mana. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/3ffdf39b9fbfcadded67e8bb11060e2a.poster.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/3ffdf39b9fbfcadded67e8bb11060e2a.webm?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>The game is <strong>narrative</strong> and <strong>exploration</strong> driven, but <strong>combats</strong> are dynamic and fun, involving the use of swords, magic and armors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/c1f7737763768d5098abe5eb9b6d81a8.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>The game includes in-game HELP POINTS for the chill players that just want to enjoy an interesting narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/b89c524b7c138d8fac20214f705ab758.poster.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/b89c524b7c138d8fac20214f705ab758.webm?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/b89c524b7c138d8fac20214f705ab758.mp4?t=1738838728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player will play as an adventurous kid that gets involved in a series of events that will affect the history of the world where he lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786980/extras/7bac3ea8bf2bc73e13106dfb071a27c0.avif?t=1738838728\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p>",
